perl5.branches 5.28
perl5.setup         PDL-Graphics-PLplot 0.74
license             {Artistic-1 GPL}
maintainers         nomaintainer
description         PDL::Graphics::PLplot -  An object-oriented interface from Perl/PDL to the PLPLOT plotting library
